108
00:07:16,300 --> 00:07:17,180
From now on,

109
00:07:17,180 --> 00:07:18,819
I won't compete with you for anything.

110
00:07:19,259 --> 00:07:21,139
Just make her spare my life!

111
00:07:21,339 --> 00:07:22,180
Guchen.

112
00:07:22,180 --> 00:07:23,759
Yixi, come down now!

113
00:07:23,779 --> 00:07:25,079
He's no threat to us.

114
00:07:25,699 --> 00:07:26,660
Come down!

115
00:07:53,500 --> 00:07:54,379
You cursed creature!

116
