134
00:08:34,679 --> 00:08:35,799
Don't touch my Xiaochuan!

135
00:08:37,799 --> 00:08:38,784
I'm sorry.

136
00:08:39,456 --> 00:08:40,416
I'm sorry.

137
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:42,200
Sorry won't fix anything!

138
00:08:44,259 --> 00:08:45,340
My Xiaochuan

139
00:08:45,919 --> 00:08:48,279
was choked to death.

140
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:50,279
He was so young.

141
00:08:50,960 --> 00:08:52,279
So kind-hearted.

142
00:08:52,919 --> 00:08:54,840
