230
00:15:46,080 --> 00:15:49,312
♪Storms disperse.
Drunken reunions trace past bonds♪

231
00:15:49,312 --> 00:15:51,968
♪Asking when we'll meet in another life♪

232
00:15:52,448 --> 00:15:55,040
♪A millennium passes in moments.
Where's today's joy♪

233
00:15:55,040 --> 00:15:58,112
