00:17:09,632 --> 00:17:15,680
♪Though countless sorrows
may fall like petals♪

256
00:17:16,128 --> 00:17:18,784
♪For this stretch of time♪

257
00:17:18,784 --> 00:17:22,944
♪Walk with you through life and death♪

258
00:17:24,700 --> 00:17:25,740
I remember now.

259
00:17:28,579 --> 00:17:29,740
I remember now.

260
00:17:31,819 --> 00:17:33,380
I remember everything now.

261
00:17:36,660 --> 00:17:38,339
So I am the true Night Deity.

262
00:17:39,940 --> 00:17:41,019
I am the one.

