265
00:17:49,619 --> 00:17:51,420
I am the Night Deity.

266
00:17:56,000 --> 00:17:57,984
♪Carving your essence in my heart♪

267
00:17:59,319 --> 00:18:00,288
Yixi.

268
00:18:01,700 --> 00:18:03,180
I'm coming to see you now.

269
00:18:19,039 --> 00:18:22,319
You were rigorously selected
by the Nine Heavens as the Sword Master,

270
00:18:22,559 --> 00:18:25,440
