279
00:18:58,160 --> 00:18:59,720
Do you think I'd still trust you?

280
00:19:00,400 --> 00:19:01,240
Wan Guchen,

281
00:19:01,920 --> 00:19:02,920
I never do things

282
00:19:03,039 --> 00:19:04,599
for personal gain.

